    "In our unified format, the output format is a JSON string with thought and tool_calls.",
    "To avoid the model overfitting on JSON format and to enable the model to follow various output formats upon different format instructions, we prepare 15 different output formats along with their corresponding format instructions and format converters.",
    "The formats include JSON, XML, YAML, plain text, etc.",
    "To further understand the data quality and to thoroughly investigate the sources of errors in the evaluation, we conduct a detailed analysis of the unified dataset.",
